%html
  %head
    %meta{charset: 'utf-8'}
    %title StreetWars Stats
    %meta{name: 'viewport', content: 'width=device-width; initial-scale=1.0; maximum-scale=1.0;'}
    %link{rel: 'stylesheet', href: '//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.1.1/css/bootstrap.min.css'}
    %link{rel: 'stylesheet', href: '/app.css'}
  %body
    .hero
      .container
        %h1.page-header StreetWars Stats
        %p
          The Mustache Mainframe&trade; (streetwars.net) is great, but it doesn't
          actually provide you a way of seeing who's the most dangerous player/team.
        %p
          This site lists everyone in StreetWars ordered by their
          %em lethality
          \- the amount of kills they've made divided by the number of people in
          their team. For example, a team with 4 people but only 1 kill is
          significantly less lethal than a solo player with 1 kill. If two teams
          have the same lethality, the bigger team will appear higher in this list as they have
          more resource to increase their killing power. Science, bitches!
        %p
          %strong
            \- the Bureau, with love

    .container
      .teams
        %p.text-center Crunching data, hold up...
        .progress.progress-striped.active
          .progress-bar{style: 'width: 100%;'}

    / yeah so this is fucking horrible
    %script{id: 'teams-template', type: 'text/x-handlebars-template'}
      {{#each teams}}
      %div{class: 'team{{#unless competing}} out{{/unless}}'}
        .row
          .col-sm-8
            %div.pull-right
              {{#if competing}}
              %span.label.label-success Competing
              {{else}}
              %span.label.label-danger Eliminated
              {{/if}}
            %h2
              {{addOne @index}} - {{name}}

            .players
              .wrapper.clearfix
                {{#each assassins}}
                %a{href: 'http://www.streetwars.net/#/games/1/a/{{assassin_token}}', target: '_blank', class: 'player {{#unless alive}}out{{/unless}}'}
                  .image
                    %img{src: '{{avatar}}'}
                  .name {{name}}
                  .kills
                    ({{kills}} kills)
                  {{#if team_leader}}
                  .leader-badge
                    %span.label.label-warning Leader
                  {{/if}}
                {{/each}}
          .col-sm-4.clearfix
            .counter
              .count {{kills}}
              %small KILLS
            {{#unless solo}}
            .counter
              .count {{size}}
              %small MEMBERS
            .counter
              .count {{alive}}
              %small ALIVE
            .counter
              .count {{dead}}
              %small DEAD
            {{/unless}}
      %hr
      {{/each}}

    %script{src: '//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js'}
    %script{src: '//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/handlebars.js/2.0.0-alpha.4/handlebars.min.js'}
    %script{src: '/app.js'}
